! Full Chat Log Dumps

Parse-friendly section for full conversation exports, session captures, and
large chat-derived research dumps.

!! Purpose

Concept tiddlers should stay small and linked. Full chat logs belong in a
manifested dump lane where they can be parsed, sampled, hashed, and mined
without turning the wiki into a transcript warehouse.

